	  symbol instead of `PPL_USE_GLPK'.  Define HAVE_GMP before
	  including <glpssx.h> and <glpk.h>, undefining it after these
	  inclusions.  The ulset() function does not exist in GLPK 4.28:
	  use xlset() instead.

