2001-11-04 Sunday 12:22  Elisa Ricci

	* src/Polyhedron.cc (1.77): In functions
	  Polyhedron::assign_variable and Polyhedron::substitute_variable
	  we must clear the flags SAT_C_UP_TO_DATE and SAT_G_UP_TO_DATE,
