	  matrix was not sorted.

2001-11-04 Sunday 10:25  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* interfaces/Prolog/SICStus/ppl_sicstus.cc (1.23):
	  ppl_intersection_assign/2 calls
